  "details": "A security flaw has been discovered in Edimax BR-6675nD 1.12. This affects the function formHwSet of the file /goform/formHwSet of the component POST Request Handler. The manipulation of the argument regDomain/ABandregDomain/nic0Addr/nic1Addr/wlanAddr/inicAddr results in command injection. It is possible to launch the attack remotely. The exploit has been released to the public and may be used for attacks. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
